features: 💡【Minimalist Style & Pull Chain Design】These 2 packs table lamps are constructed of cream fabric lampshades and wood-like metal bases, combined with minimalist and modern styles, making the lamps sleek and elegant. What’s more, these lamps for bedside are coming with a stylish pull chain design, makes them easy to control, convenient for daily application.

💡【Dual USB Ports & Convenient Charging】The modern desk lamp has dual 5V/2.1A USB charging ports so that you can charge two electronic devices at the same time, such as mobile phones, iPad, earphones, speakers and e-books and so the like. No matter whether the small table lamp is on or off, the ports still supply power to your devices. Great to free up your space and settle the trouble of lack of sockets on the wall.

💡【Superior Material & Eye Caring】Our ideal USB nightstand lamps are made with vivid metal base in wooden color and high-quality fabric shade, oak metal can prevent the desk reading lamps from rusting and easy to clean, the cream fabric lampshade gives a soft glow to you while maintaining the true color of the bulb. Effectively reduce the strong lighting and protect your eyes.

💡【E26 Bulb Base & Easy Installation】These contemporary pull chain lamps come with standard E26 bulb sockets, suitable for medium base light bulbs in different shapes or colors, simple to create desired according to your demand. Also, the table lamps for living room are super easy to install, only need three steps within a few minutes to assemble. Please noted that the bulb is not included and needs to be purchased separately. (Max. 100W for incandescent bulbs but 8W for LED ones)

💡【Widely Application & Ideal Gifts】 The bedroom lamps for nightstand set of 2 have cream fabric shades and a wooden-like metal base, minimalist style makes it a great decor for your space. You can place these ideal decorative lamps in various places, such as dorm, offices, nursery, bedroom, living room, nightstand, sofa tables and etc.. Because of the stylish appearance and multiple functions, the usb lamp sets are also a great gift choice for your friends and family on the special occasions.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 25, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Nice lamps at a great price
reviews.reviewText: Nicely made product. The chain feature is useful. Works well for modern decor. Recommended product!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 6, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars lightweight and perfect for our needs (UPDATE: one of them broke!)
reviews.reviewText: very lightweight - clearly cheaply made, but they look and feel great. love the USB (just don't tug too hard, cause the lamp will come flying with it!) - Nov 6th, 2023UPDATE, Nov 30, 2023: Unfortunately, one of the strings broke off, rendering the entire lamp useless and broken. a bit disappointed with this, as the other lamp's string doesn't seem to have the same issue so now we only have one out of the two. PS - we weren't being heavy-handed! like i said, the other lamp doesn't seem to have the issue.i saw other reviewers have this problem. If this is a reoccurring issue, I recommend to the manufacturers to include a flip-switch somewhere on the base so customers could keep using the lamp, even if the string breaks.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 31, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Very Cute Lamps!
reviews.reviewText: I absolutely LOVE these lamps! They were so easy to put together. They did not come with light bulbs but the bulbs I got were bright LEDs and they are perfect for reading or just as a desk lamp.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 4, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Does not come with bulbs. Small and exactly what I was looking for for my guest room. The shades are a nice brownish linen color.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 1, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These will light up the space around them.
reviews.reviewText: They have a nice design and when you turn them on with a bulb in them, they will light up the space.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 30, 2023
reviews.reviewText: Perfect for our bedside lamps. Nice quality. Great value. Look much more expensive than they were. I would highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 3, 2023
reviews.reviewText: These are so cute. They are a little smaller, which is what I wanted for our nightstands. They agave easy on and off buttons and they were super easy to put together. I would highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 22, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Not bad for the price but seen better
reviews.reviewText: Pros:Convenience: The lamps come equipped with two USB ports, which allow you to charge your devices while you use them, making them ideal for bedside tables or desks.Design: The lamps have a modern design with a cream fabric shade and a wood color base, which adds a touch of elegance to any room.Adjustable Lighting: The lamps have a pull chain that allows you to adjust the brightness of the lamp to your liking.Versatility: These lamps can be used in a variety of settings such as living rooms, bedrooms, offices, reading areas, dorms, and hotels.Cons:Quality of Construction: The build quality of these lamps may not be as sturdy as more expensive models.Light Quality: The lampshades may not provide the best light quality, as they can be a bit opaque and may not allow all of the light to pass through.Bulb Compatibility: These lamps are only compatible with E26 bulbs, which may limit your options if you prefer a different type of bulb.Overall, the Set of 2 Table Lamps with 2 USB Ports is a great choice if you're looking for a convenient and stylish lighting solution. The USB ports are a useful feature, and the modern design fits well with many different decors. However, the build quality may not be as durable as more expensive models, and the light quality may not be as good as other options.
